| Element | Symbol | Purpose |
|--------|--------|--------|
| **System** | `âŸ¦ âŸ§` | Encapsulates any entity, process, or structure |
| **Interaction** | `â†’`, `âŸ·`, `âˆ®` | Denotes flow, coupling, or feedback |
